From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: MC20018 <winme2001@outlook.com>
Date: Mon, 8 Jun 2026 13:22:29 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Expand ecosystem event hooks

Add vanilla hook points for fine-grained player, entity, block, inventory, world, and server events.

Route gameplay mutations through Fand bridge classes so plugins can observe, cancel, or adjust high-value actions such as projectile launches, explosions, workstation results, redstone updates, sign changes, login checks, and server-list pings.

